  "Description": {
    "English": "A living, fertile egg, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">ready to hatch!</span><br><br>The weight inside this egg shifts constantly, as though the creature within is bouncing energetically.<br><br>Scans indicate the being within has the genetic potential to be an <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">adventurous</span> companion, curious to explore planets beyond its frozen homeworld.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一颗活生生的受精卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">已经准备好孵化！</span><br><br>这颗卵不停晃动，仿佛里面的生物正在兴奋地摇摆。<br><br>根据扫描结果显示，里面的生物拥有特殊的基因潜质，如果好好培养，日后将成为得力的<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">冒险</span>同伴。它十分渴望外出探索冰封母星之外的万千世界。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一個有生命的受精卵，<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">且準備孵化！！</span><br><br>蛋內的重量不停變動，就像裡面的生物正在激烈地跳動一般。<br><br>掃描結果顯示，該生物可能擁有以下特徵：<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">愛冒險</span>的同伴，樂於探索冰寒家園以外的星球。"
  },
